            <p class="lh-lg fs-5 px-1 px-sm-1 px-md-5 px-lg-5">&nbsp; Established in 2014 as Turtle Creek Pub, LLC and operated for a little over
                a
                year. What
                was once Mikes Pizza & Fortell's Pizza Den, was transformed into the atmosphere Turtle Creek is
                today
                and
                what you'll enjoy when you visit! On July 11, 2015, we turned the key to what is now Turtle Creek
                Pub &
                Grill and have made it a Destination, for lunch, dinner or to just have fun!
                We try to keep things Special when we're open Starting with Sunday Fundays! Enjoy game specials
                along
                with
                our 1/2 price select Bottles of Wine!
                Tuesday Nights are <span style="color:blue">Karaoke Nights</span> and some great voices...(And some Not so Great), head for the
                CREEK
                and
                Let it All Out! Always a fun night and the tunes from the KJ are from 7 - 11!
                Wednesday Nights we bring you <span style="color:red">Xtreme Bar Bingo</span> (21 & up), where you can win a Weekly Jackpot which
                is
                NEVER
                less than $3000, Big Screen TVs, <span style="color: red">Cardinal</span> or <span class="color: blue"> Blues</span> Tickets and MORE Really Cool Prizes!
                That brings us to Steak Thursdays, where we off our Selection of the Week which could be a NY Strip,
                Filet
                or maybe Sirloin...cooked the Way you like!
                And of course our Week-ends are always filled with some of THE BEST Music around!
                YES! We LOVE SPORTS and our hearts are with Our <span style="color: red">CARDINALS</span>, <span style="color: blue"> BLUES</span> and we are an "Official <span style="color: green">GREEN BAY
                PACKER</span>",
                Venue where you'll always find a House Full of <span style="color: green">Ch</span><span style="color: gold">ee</span><span style="color:green">seh</span><span style="color:gold">ea</span><span style="color: green">ds</span> from all over for every game! Our Kitchen, Pub and Wait staff are top notch who will make your time spent with us even better with personal and attentive service! Turtle Creek Pub & Grill has fast become that destination where people feel comfortable and know they'll have a good time regardless of what's on the schedule with some of that Great Music we bring you every Week-end! Our Large Open Air Patio is one of a kind that allows you to soak up the sun or enjoy an evening breeze under the stars while savoring your favorite item from our menu & bar. We know you'll enjoy your experience with us and know you'll come back bringing friends to share what you've already discovered!
                <br>
                <strong>&nbsp; Thank you for your support, patronage and choosing Turtle Creek Pub & Grill! Melissa & Todd, Owners</strong>
